Frequently Asked Questions

What are your response times?

Email responses within 24 hours, phone support during working hours, WhatsApp for urgent queries.

Do you have a physical office?

Our main office is at ICP Petrapole. You can also reach us through our online support channels.

Can I visit the office?

Yes, you can visit during working hours. Please call ahead for scheduled appointments.

Do you provide on-site support?

Yes, we have support staff available at the terminal for real-time assistance.
